metadata.title: Diets of the Important Groundfish in the Aleutian Islands in Summer 1991.

creators.name: Atmospheric Administration (NOAA), National Marine Fisheries Service (NMFS)

metadata.description: The diets of commercially important Groundfish species in the waters surrounding the Aleutian Islands during the summer of 1991 were studied. Important prey types, predator-prey size relationships, and prey distribution are discussed in detail.
metadata.notes:
Purpose: To report on the diets of the important Groundfish in the Aleutian Islands in summer 1991.
